Save to /Users/joshuadavis/Documents/Claude/Projects/Valley Pawn Studios/output/{YYYY-MM-DD}/deals_social_manifest_{YYYY-MM-DD}.json with per-store scheduled_for + Publer post IDs + skipped stores.

